Program: Crossing Continents
Title: The Kingdom of Kids
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00jdb6f
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 6 Apr 2009
Bill Law reports from Swaziland, a country laid waste by poverty and AIDS. Impoverished children, with the help of surviving adults and local NGOs, are learning how to read and write in informal schools. In a country with a falling population and an economy in freefall, the children of Swaziland, against all the odds, are battling for their future and taking control of their own fates. Show less